## Limitations and Open Questions

- XAI scores use TF-IDF as a bag-of-words proxy.  Semantic nuances not
  captured by lexical overlap may not be reflected in attribution scores.
- For production deployments, complement these scores with embedding-based
  context attribution (``context_relevance_embedding`` metric) where a live
  embedding model is available.
- Human review and legal/compliance sign-off are required before deployment.

